metadata.name: Lost in Fantasy
metadata.description:
This art is our first collaboration with Rina. We tried to combine our two styles and create something mysterious and magical! Also we both love cats, so we decided to create a mystical animals that bursts out of a fairy tale book. We are planning more works for our "The Mysterious Side" collection soon! In the meantime, we have a question for you:
What would it look like, if you too, could bring fantasy into the real world?

Art size: 7000 x 7000 px
*As a gift to the buyer, we will send a physical poster with our signatures.
